query:
SELECT 
                    t.id, 
                    t.label, 
                    t.color
                FROM tag t
                LEFT JOIN tag_to_session tts ON t.id = tts.tag_id
                WHERE t.created_by = $1
                GROUP BY t.id, t.label, t.color
                ORDER BY COUNT(tts.tag_id) DESC
                LIMIT 1
